name: Play it Loud
description: Alana, the web3girl has just been born on the 21st of July 2021. Her desires to explore different realms of music, art, and everything else the blockchain has to offer are sheer endless. Alana x Play it fuckin loud offers a glimpse into her world through a tiny window, showing her in a relaxed state and letting her mind flow along with the rockinÂ´ tunes of the surrounding speaker walls. This piece belongs to a continuing series of works that accompany Alana on her travels through different realms of the metaverse and show her understanding and appreciation of her surroundings. Collaboration between Stella Achenbach and Tania MV Studio.
